node.text: #CNN Reporter: "During the last eight hours, the time that we've been waiting here, we have not seen a single U.S. flight evacuate people. We saw one U.S. flight took off about half an hour to an hour ago but it was filled with U.S. servicemen and women." … Did #JoeBiden completely abandon and give up being President?  This is such an embarrassment for our country and especially to the watchful eyes of the international community. What’s the hold up, #SleepyJoe. Also where is #KamalaHarris? She is in compete hiding, just like his #presssecretary #JenPsaki. #comeonman

node.title: CNN: During Last 8 Hours, Not a Single U.S. Flight has Evacuated People

They cater to like-minded individuals and pass off their opinions as facts. That’s why they are so distrusted and that’s why they are #fakenews #thisiscnn #veryfakenews #reliablesources

node.title: “Most People Don’t Want to Turn to Brian Stelter to Tell us What’s Real….”

node.text:
#SanFrancisco Police: 

“We’ve seen a rise in violent attacks by homeless individuals, including attacks on #policeofficers. We are deeply grateful to these citizens who rushed to our officer’s aide. Our staffing shortage left this officer working alone instead of with a partner.” 

Everyone should be thankful to police officers for everything they have to deal with, including mentally ill individuals living on the street — all while leftists want to defund or abolish them.  What a “woke” joke. 

#bluelivesmatter #backtheblue #backtheblue💙 #lawenforcement

node.title: Homeless Man Attacks Short-Staffed Female Police Officer, Citizens Help 💙

node.text:
#CNN “reporter” asks #KarenFann — #Arizona State Senator who is conducting an audit of the 2020 election in her state. Watch as the CNN reporter (and then the anchors) fight aggressively to convince themselves that potential fraud should not be investigated. If they were reporting on #DonaldTrump’s second term I’ll bet they would be extremely interested in potential fraud. They also took shots at OAN. 

“Are you saying that #OAN is not a credible news source?”

CNN Reporter: “YASSS.” 

… Saying OAN is not credible is pretty funny coming from CNN …

node.title: CNN Confronts AZ State Senator in Charge of Election Audit in Arizona

node.text: Here’s what France did. French security police have run a convoy of their French & Afghan families from their embassy in the #Kabul green zone up to the Kabul airport. The families have since been evacuated.  British troops have likewise run several operations to get their citizens out. I really hope that’s what we’re doing… right?  I hope #JoeBiden’s state dept isn’t charging American citizens $2000+ for a plane ride back to the states… Because that would just be absolutely abhorrent considering many of them can’t even get into the airport 🤔 All of this didn’t need to be such a scramble. This will forever define #SleepyJoe’s Presidency. This major fumble will be his legacy.
